  "plan": "Ranger Thane acts first per initiative. He will loose a longbow shot at the lead sahuagin (the priestess), using his first attack preroll. No other NPCs or monsters act yet. Initiative stops at Eirik Hearthwise (player). Initiative order window processed: [Ranger Thane].",
